  "description": "A silhouette of a bridge spans across dark waters under a dramatically fiery red and orange sky. The bridge appears to be an older structure with visible support pillars and a suspended roadway. There's a smaller, arched structure visible near the left edge of the water, possibly a remnant of the original bridge. Distant lights are visible on the water, appearing as faint, small green and white spots. The sky is filled with rich hues of red and orange, suggesting a sunset or sunrise, and has subtle cloud formations. The overall scene evokes a sense of tranquility and nostalgia.",
